# ── Rust ──────────────────────────────────────────────
/target
**/target
# Keep Cargo.lock COMMITTED for the app crates — it pins the exact build.

# ── WASM build output ─────────────────────────────────
# Generated by wasm-pack; rebuilt from source.
# Both forms: trailing-slash matches dirs, bare name matches symlinks.
client-wasm/pkg
client-wasm/pkg/
pkg/
**/pkg/
*.wasm

# ── SpacetimeDB generated client bindings ─────────────
# COMMITTED (not ignored): the frontend build imports these and CI has no
# spacetime CLI to regenerate them. They change only on a schema edit —
# regenerate with `npm run gen` (spacetime generate) and commit the diff.

# ── Frontend / bundler ────────────────────────────────
# Both forms: trailing-slash matches dirs, bare name matches symlinks
# (worktrees symlink node_modules to the main checkout's copy).
node_modules
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo
coverage/

# ── Playwright (multi-window e2e) output ──────────────
test-results/
playwright-report/
blob-report/
.playwright/

# ── Python (tooling/scripts) ──────────────────────────
__pycache__/
.venv/

# ── Code knowledge graph index (codebase-memory-mcp) ──
# Derived index — never commit.
.codebase-memory/
.codebase-memory-mcp/

# ── Secrets & env ─────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── SpacetimeDB CLI scratch config ────────────────────
# Auto-generated by the `spacetime` CLI; we pass explicit flags instead.
spacetime.json
spacetime.local.json

# ── Derived agent tooling ─────────────────────────────
# Skills vendored via `npx skills add` (reinstall from skills-lock.json). The
# curated *.md skills under .claude/skills/ are tracked; the pixijs* entries are
# derived symlinks into .agents/.
.agents/
.claude/skills/pixijs*
# MCP server config — machine-specific / regenerable doc-fetch servers.
.mcp.json
# Local Claude Code state (shared .claude/settings.json stays tracked).
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── cargo-mutants output ──────────────────────────────
# Regenerated on each nightly run; ~11M artifact — never commit.
mutants.out/

# ── OS / editor ───────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.swp
*.log
